<h1></h1>    Header 1 - large text

<h2></h2>    Header 2 

<h3></h3>    Header 3 

<p></p>      Paragraph

<img src="" width="">          Image Tag (self closing tag) with source to render and width to adjust the size to browser (recommended)\

<div></div>     divider - and what ever that is inside is children

<button></button>

<input type="specify the type of input here (text, number, password, date, time, color, file)" placeholder="give user what data we are asking for">

<a href="insert link here" target="_blank to open new tab"></a>     (links) Anchor tags - used to link to another page


<!doctype html> Tells the browswer we are using HTML 5 - metadata for the browswer
<html> this wraps everything </html>
<head> This is where we add metadata (styles)</head>
<body> This is used</body>

<ol>Number Ordered List </ol>
<ul>bullet points - Unordered List </ul>

<li>List tag</li>

selector - selects which tags it applies to (eg. body tag)


body {    ---> selector
    background: yellow;     --->     property: Value
}


hex codes uses RGB


Display: inline -- displays item horizontally

Display: block -- displays vertically (stacks on top)
